## Usage Guidelines

### Canvas & Workspace
- Use **True Black** (#0a0a0a) for the main canvas - maximum contrast
- Use **Elevated Black** (#141414) for floating panels and toolbars
- Grid dots in **Neural Gray** (#2d2d2d) at 10% opacity for orientation

### Node Design
- Base: **Surface Black** (#1a1a1a) with semantic color top bar
- Border: 1px of semantic color at 60% opacity
- Hover: Increase border opacity to 100% + add glow
- Active: Full glow effect + particle systems

### Connections
- Inactive: **Connection Gray** (#4a5568) at 40% opacity
- Hover: Semantic color at 60% opacity
- Active: Semantic color at 100% + flow animation
- Thickness: 1-4px based on data volume
- Confidence: Opacity 40-100% based on score

### Typography on Dark Canvas
- Primary text: **Pure White** (#ffffff)
- Secondary text: **Neural Gray** (#a0a0a0)
- Accent text: Semantic colors at 100% opacity
- Disabled text: **Connection Gray** (#4a5568)

